questionsAndAnswers.question: Why should I choose you over the competition?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We are passionate about our work and helping your application idea succeed and have the experience to make it happen. Weve worked huge UK and USA Based Companies. The experience from all the successful projects gives us the ability to provide creative and a streamlined process.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is the price & timeframe?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Its depend on the complexity of work,All projects are priced differently. It can vary from $5 to $5000 - it depends on the content & the pages you need. Contact me and discuss these things in details.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you support me once the project will be delivered?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. I can support you for bug fixing or problem you have. Or in the future you want me to add new features in your project.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you make websites responsive?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. Our websites are responsive to all the devices like mobiles, tables , laptop and desktops.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you convert PSD to HTML or Bootstrap?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: yes but first please share the PSD file with me So that we can get the complexity of work.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I am interested in your gig. Can I order it?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. But, first make sure you contacted me to see if we are able to do your job. It saves us both a lot of time and money!

reviews_snippet.comment: Faizan's work on my Bootstrap website was exceptional. He flawlessly transformed my vision into a responsive, visually stunning site. His dedication, expertise, and effective communication made the entire process a pleasure. I'm thrilled with the outstanding results and highly recommend Faizan for top-tier web development. Will recommend him to all of my Company friends and will come back for more projects as he is a top tier Developer. Thank you very much
One of the best on Fiverr. Great communication, excellent work with fast delivery..He is now my go to guy from now on..

Amazing Service, Quality and time. definitely recommend for anyone that are looking getting their work done, professionally fast and great communication skills.
Now we are working on our next project.

Faizan is very responsive and professional. He is very competent and was able to answer every question and make every edit I needed. He and his team goes over and beyond to make sure everything is how we need it. Even after the delivery of our website he was only a message away if we need any assistance.

Faizan helped us improving our event webpage. Since I know that many competitor web pages are of very varying quality and clarity, I expected this to not be a straight forward project. However, after some initial chats and suggestions, Faizan did a thorough research about similar industry pages and the result was excellent. He was very responsive, came with own suggestions and ideas, and we are very satisfied with the results. We are looking forward to the next gig with him.
